definitions.definition: A greaser or biker ; a member of any alternative subculture , as opposed to a chav or townie .
definitions.label_groups: slang , UK , countable , chiefly West Midlands

definitions.definition: A member of a United Kingdom subculture of the late 1980s and early 1990s, musically affiliated with garage rock and electronica , typically wearing baggy clothes and hair in high ponytails .
A short-lived subgenre of alternative rock music in the late 1980s and early 1990s, with influences from punk rock, electronic dance music, hip-hop , and psychedelia.
